-- Countrywide drops on FBI probe report
-- 
-- Mon Mar 10, 2008 9:06am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/03/10/us-markets-stocks-countrywide-idUSN1041955920080310

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Countrywide Financial Corp CFC.N fell 7 percent to $4.72 before the bell on Monday after the New York Times reported that the Federal Bureau of Investigation has begun a criminal inquiry of the largest U.S. mortgage lender. 

 (Reporting by  Ellis Mnyandu ; Editing by Theodore d'Afflisio)